{
  "stem": "20684.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a combination of the borders that were taken and checked here and checked.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was all money, you see.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a game.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They could put us in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't because we were criminal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We crossed the borders illegally, but you pay.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They come every day, Americans come with trucks, military men carrying money in suitcases.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Come your turn and you get out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If you're important, you get out quickly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We weren't all that important, so we stayed there for about a week in Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Plenty of food, no problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was after the war, it was all right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we went to Stuttgart.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why went to Stuttgart?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because a lot of people from Radom went to Stuttgart, apparently.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were reunited with a lot of children from Radom.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some I knew, most I didn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And altogether, there were 27 children that supposedly have survived the war in the orphanage up in Stuttgart from Radom. 27 children out of a population of Radom and all its surrounding, which was 87,000, which would have been about 30,000 children, 27 survived.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it's one child in 1,000, one child in 1,200.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, this is why I was saying that you grow up very quickly, you see.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The children that survived, of course, a lot of luck has to be, as well.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Many of these children come from Russia, so only about half or a quarter of those children survive in actual Poland itself.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you get about six children in the 27,000 that survive in Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They are lucky and other things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You grow up quickly and sort of you get away with just-- you duck the bullets and keep away from the dogs and get killed and you survive.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
